'''蒽醌-2-磺酸'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>14</sub>H<sub>8</sub>O<sub>5</sub>S，它可由[[蒽醌|蒽醌]]和[[硫酸|硫酸]]在[[汞|汞]]的存在下反应制得。<ref>Meyer, Andre. Sulfonation of anthraquinone in the presence of mercury. ''Compt. rend.'', 1927. 184: 609-611.</ref>它和[[氢氧化钠|氢氧化钠]]反应，可以得到[[蒽醌-2-磺酸钠|蒽醌-2-磺酸钠]]。它和[[五氯化磷|五氯化磷]]反应，可以得到蒽醌-2-磺酰氯。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=European Journal of Medicinal Chemistry|volume=42|issue=6|language=en|date=2007-06|pages=752–771|doi=10.1016/j.ejmech.2006.12.039|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0223523407000980|title=Design, synthesis and biological evaluation of new oligopyrrole carboxamides linked with tricyclic DNA-intercalators as potential DNA ligands or topoisomerase inhibitors|accessdate=2021-01-29|author=Marie-Hélène David-Cordonnier, Marie-Paule Hildebrand, Brigitte Baldeyrou, Amelie Lansiaux, Christoph Keuser, Kerstin Benzschawel, Thomas Lemster, Ulf Pindur}}</ref>

